{"tid":916510,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"唔好屌謙叔喇，不如欣賞下周耀輝","createTime":"2018-11-25T18:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T18:20:09.000Z","uid":41237,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"74ed638bc0c3b5a61a5c2de4b523b2e3275dc080","tid":916510,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T18:54:49.000Z","msg":"「我現時自己肯做飯」做hook line，屌都費事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難得咁多愛歌知音，J下靚詞好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔離講緊林若寧，諗住呢邊特登開個周耀輝吹奏post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4405c8ac9f1923b0d0de6b3cbd7170fd99028b","tid":916510,"uid":41237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T18:58:39.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多，直接借火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「剛剛要去便利店裡 為著香煙無人點火<br />\n湊巧你正走出路上 搖搖盪盪<br />\n明明喊過不借得太多 也想借點火<br />\n就算不說一句都很清楚 雙方都經過太多<br />\n<br />\n只要接近 別無期望<br />\n夜了看電視的光<br />\n只要我們不問為何 然後直至忘記誰是我<br />\n一起靜靜的過<br />\n不需要太認識我」<br />\n<br />\n數過，四啖氣直落副歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對於填詞人來講，就係斷句下功夫<br />\n平時有啲拍子可以跟到<br />\n旋律越單調 52個字要自己間開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df4a0997031f823324258e8bfbede2346137808","tid":916510,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T18:59:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718f4ec1d8c9d8087f33f9179cc73870b73f794a","tid":916510,"uid":135265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"Why隻碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji